      <section eId="sec_CCP-4851">
        <num>CCP 4851</num>
        <heading>4851. Â Venue</heading>
        <subsection eId="CCP-4851__subsec_A">
          <num>A.</num>
          <content>
            <p>The rules of venue provided in Articles 41 through 45, 71 through 79 and 81, and 121 through 124 apply to suits brought in the parish court.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-4851__subsec_B">
          <num>B.</num>
          <content>
            <p>The rules of venue provided in Articles 41 through 45, 71 through 79 and 121 through 124 apply to suits brought in city court, except that where these articles use the word &quot;parish&quot; it shall be construed to mean the territorial jurisdiction of the city court.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=112095</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
